column5: I am trying out IE 8 right now and I have to admit, I think its really good! Very fast, no compatibality problems yet!
Which version of windows are you using?... vista, xp....?
Glen it's for Windows XP.... New version free for download off the net!!
I did some testing when it was in beta and it had some issues then. I see they are now in RC1 so I guess I'll have to try it out again.
Its supposed to even be W3C compliant !! Hmm...we need a fainting emoticon. As long as it is still tied into the ActiveX I won't touch it unless I have to.
